Global DGA Monitors for Power Transformers Market Insights
DGA Monitors for Power Transformers Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

DGA Monitors for Power Transformers Market Overview
The global market for DGA monitors for power transformers is experiencing significant growth, driven by the increasing demand for reliable power infrastructure. The market is projected to grow at a steady pace due to the rising need for efficient monitoring systems in power transmission and distribution networks. With power transformers being critical to the stability of power systems, the DGA (Dissolved Gas Analysis) monitoring technology offers crucial insights into the health of transformers, thereby preventing failures and improving operational efficiency. The market value of DGA monitors for power transformers was estimated to be USD 950 million in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 6.5% during the forecast period (2025-2032).

